字之謎，她說：「其實我當年攞身份證嗰陣一直冇發覺，原來喺嗰刻已經寫錯咗，到我參選，我仲問大會做乜寫錯我名，佢哋話係跟住我身份證咁寫，我先發覺寫錯咗，我遲啲會去改番！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來佢文盲"},{"pid":"4f0341c650034c6b96160306ed01bc9ae52b8ddf","tid":385990,"uid":39200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T04:49:18.000Z","msg":"細哨都選到 Miss HK <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}